title: Torrent Search 5.0
description:
Torrent Search 5.0 is a Torrent Search application by Plenty of Torrents that works with your Firefox or Internet Explorer browser. It makes finding torrents easier and also has many other useful gadgets such as a torrent rss feed, live tv, radio email notifier for gmail, hotmail, yahoo and more. Leave a comment and +1 if you like it.
